{"name":"Blue Magery (Ex) - Gunmage","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"blue-magery\">Blue Magery (Ex)</h3><p>At 1st level, the gun mage loses natural prowess blue magery but gains access to the following:</p><ul style=\"border-collapse: separate; \"><li><em>Magic Shot:</em> While the gun mages gun is imbued with power from the mage bullets, he can fire non-elemental bullets instead of regular ammunition. A non-elemental bullet deals 1d4 points of non-elemental damage for every time this blue magery is selected. Non-elemental bullets do not use black powder or ammunition and count as magic for the purpose of bypassing damage reduction.</li></ul><p>This ability modifies blue magery.</p><h3>Original Blue Magery(trimmed)</h3><p>At 1st level and every four blue mage levels thereafter, a blue mage increases her power with her spells of 1st level or higher. This ability applies only to spells that she casts as a blue mage, not to those she might have by virtue of levels in another class. At each such opportunity, she can choose from the list of the following (with a maximum of 2 per):</p><ul><li><em>Analysis Mastery:</em> This grants a +2 bonus to Knowledge checks for Analysis abilities. The first time the blue mage chooses this ability, Analysis requires only a move action to use. The second time the blue mage chooses this ability, Analysis requires only a swift action to use.</li><li><em>Creature Knowledge Mastery:</em> This provides a +2 insight bonus on all saving throws from creatures that have been <em>Scanned.</em> In addition, the blue mage may reroll any failed Knowledge check once per round.</li><li><em>Obscure Spell Mastery:</em> This increases the DC for all of the blue mages spells by 1 as well as increases the difficulty in identifying her spells via Spellcraft skill by 2.</li></ul><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/archetypes/gun-mage/\">Link to Ability on FFd20</a> This version updated on 02/08/2024</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Blue Mage"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":false,"prf":false,"pil":false,"pro":false,"rep":false,"rid":false,"sen":false,"slt":false,"spl":false,"ste":false,"sur":false,"swm":false,"umd":false},"currency":{"pp":{},"gp":{},"sp":{},"cp":{}},"altCurrency":{"pp":{},"gp":{},"sp":{},"cp":{}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.7","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1679205924106,"modifiedTime":1707448210445,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"_id":"xPKhIDtyGTx1Wubd"}
{"_id":"z3wlpasYIuZYECIz","name":"Azure Talent: Concentrate","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The blue mage can reroll any concentration check she has just made with a +4 bonus. She must use this ability after the roll is made, but before the roll&rsquo;s outcome is determined. The blue mage must take the second roll, even if it is worse. The blue mage can use this ability once per day.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6400; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Link to Azure Talents on FFd20</span></p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Azure Talent"],"actions":[{"_id":"Pg2iMIWmhTDNPXlB","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special","unchained":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"day","value":1,"maxFormula":"","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":[],"attackNotes":[],"soundEffect":"","powerAttack":{"multiplier":"","damageBonus":2,"critMultiplier":1},"naturalAttack":{"primaryAttack":true,"secondary":{"attackBonus":"-5","damageMult":0.5}},"nonlethal":false,"touch":false,"usesAmmo":false,"spellEffect":"","spellArea":"","conditionals":[],"enh":{"value":null}}],"uses":{"per":"day","value":1,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFl